snippet.title: Faaast Penguin | LAAAUNCH Trailer
snippet.description:
Play for Free with Cross-Platform Support!
Faaast Penguin is now available on Steam, Epic Games Store, and PlayStation 5!
*Nintendo Switch and Xbox Series X|S versions coming soon!

Faaast Penguin is a survival action racing game for up to 40 players!
Use attacks, shortcuts, and Ultimate Rides to reach the finish line faster than anyone else!

#FaaastPenguin
